      "content": "but i dont have insurance and the private hospitals here are super expensive... i mean, its just a kitchen knife, it isnt like i sliced an artery or anything. the honey thing is a real thing used in medical settings for wound care right? if i just use medical grade honey and keep it really clean, can't i just manage it myself for a night and see how it looks in the morning?",
